Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.18,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all couples around here. \NOnly the lame guys are by themselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, miss.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She got one! {lit: caught - meaning got him to pick her up}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect match.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally Ako's type.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A model, right? {model-san}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.73,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.56,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in some modeling club, right? \NAre you not?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.95,0:15:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Knew it! \NYou're different from the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught on quick.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Professional photographer?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. How about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try working for me \Nin secret from your agency?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just the kind I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.90,0:15:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry for the late introduction. I'm Kondo. {kondooo desu was a shtick of https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Masaomi_Kond%C5%8D}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? It's Kanda-san! {yes, a totally unrelated guy, not the same kondo}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.06,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, over there! Kanda-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanda-san, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanda-san, an autograph, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.97,0:15:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{Kanda-san, wait!}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.74,0:15:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.87,0:16:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I ruined your clothes. \NLet me get you some new ones.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.63,0:16:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really fine. I'm actually playing the Cinderella Game with my friends right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I mean I'm supposed \Nto meet up with my friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.73,0:16:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't feel right if I don't. \NWhy don't you get in the car?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be shy. \NLet's get in the car.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should just go home?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.79,0:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my studio.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on in, make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.48,0:16:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.72,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.30,0:17:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.45,0:17:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.97,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In love with me already? {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.90,0:17:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait here a sec. I'll buy you new clothes and come right back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.40,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
