Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.84,0:19:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.64,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't met since our elementary school graduation, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in a place like this?
